<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id628594af-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s1963"><num value="1963">§ 1963.</num><heading> Severability</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">If any provision of this chapter or the applicability thereof is held invalid, the remaining provisions of this chapter shall not be affected thereby.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id628594b0-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/608/tIV/s403">Pub. L. 95–608, title IV, § 403</ref>, <date date="1978-11-08">Nov. 8, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3078">92 Stat. 3078</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
